OL,3,CMan who made nearly #500,000 running
OL,4,Cillegal TV streaming company sentenced
OL,6,FA Co Londonderry man who made nearly
OL,7,Fhalf a million pounds and enjoyed a
OL,8,F"lavish" lifestyle running an illegal
OL,9,FTV streaming company has been
OL,10,Fsentenced to four years.
OL,12,FThe judge told 38-year-old Cormac
OL,13,FMcGuckin, who has 25 previous
OL,14,Fconvictions, "you caused harm to
OL,15,Fcompanies like Sky and BT. Your
OL,16,Fmotives were purely financial. You
OL,17,Fmade a great deal of money".
