OL,3,CMan who made nearly #500,000 running
OL,4,Cillegal TV streaming company sentenced
OL,6,FMcGuckin, of the Meadows in Bellaghy,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to a number of fraud
OL,8,Fcharges, dating back to 2016, in June
OL,9,F2024 and will spend two years in
OL,10,Fprison and two years out on licence.
OL,12,FHe looked at his wife who was also in
OL,13,Fthe dock before he was lead away.
OL,15,FMaura McGuckin, 34, with the same
OL,16,Faddress, was handed a suspended
OL,17,Fsentence for her part after also
OL,18,Fpleading guilty in June.
