OL,3,CMan who made nearly #500,000 running
OL,4,Cillegal TV streaming company sentenced
OL,6,FAt Omagh Crown Court, the judge told
OL,7,Fthe mother of four "you sat back and
OL,8,Fbenefited from your husband's
OL,9,Fdishonesty. You are before this court
OL,10,Fbecause of his actions".
OL,12,FThe illegal streaming business was
OL,13,Fexposed by an undercover internet
OL,14,Finvestigator.
OL,16,FThe court heard that in the pre-
OL,17,Fsentence report McGuckin "believed it
OL,18,Fwas a victimless crime and he wasn't
OL,19,Fharming anyone".
