OL,3,CMan who made nearly #500,000 running
OL,4,Cillegal TV streaming company sentenced
OL,6,FHis wife said she "didn't realise what
OL,7,Fher husband was doing was illegal. She
OL,8,Fwas oblivious to the money coming into
OL,9,Fthe joint account and was happy to
OL,10,Fturn a blind eye as long as no one
OL,11,Fcame knocking".
OL,13,FThe court heard the couple had a
OL,14,Flavish lifestyle in terms of owning
OL,15,Fhigh end cars and going on expensive
OL,16,Fholidays.
