OL,6,FIn a statement, Matt Hibbert, Group
OL,7,FDirector Anti-Piracy at Sky, said: "We
OL,8,Fare grateful to FACT and the Police
OL,9,FService of Northern Ireland in
OL,10,Fsuccessfully bringing this case to
OL,11,Fcourt.
OL,13,F"We work closely with our partners in
OL,14,Ftracking down those who are intent on
OL,15,Fstealing our content and in helping
OL,16,Fkeep consumers safe from the risks of
OL,17,Fillegal streaming, such as malware,
OL,18,Faccessing banking information or theft
OL,19,Fof personal data."
